Acer held its Next at Acer event in New York on 11 April 2019, where it took the opportunity to show off its new laptops, desktop PCs, displays, and Chromebooks. The event was held at the Duggal Greenhouse, and MyBroadband attended the event courtesy of Acer South Africa. Following a keynote presentation by Acer CEO Jason Chen, guests were invited to take a look at all the new hardware on display – and try it out for themselves. To show you what went down at Next at Acer 2019, we have compiled photos from the event below. How does one get to a PC hardware event? By water taxi, of course. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-302666" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Acer0937.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="480" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Acer0937.jpg 1200w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Acer0937-533x400.jpg 533w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Acer0937-768x576.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Acer0937-573x430.jpg 573w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> The event was held at the Duggal Greenhouse in New York. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-302668" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Acer0939.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="480" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Acer0939.jpg 1200w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Acer0939-533x400.jpg 533w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Acer0939-768x576.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Acer0939-573x430.jpg 573w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-302670" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Acer0940.jpg" alt="" width